    DASH --> DASH_API
    CLAIMS --> SCORE_API
    CLAIMS --> PROV_API
    CLAIMS --> CLAIMS_API
    CHAT_UI --> CHAT_API
    FAIR_UI --> FAIR_API
    SEARCH --> PROV_API

    SCORE_API --> SCORING
    CHAT_API --> AI
    DASH_API --> PG
    FAIR_API --> FAIRNESS
    GRAPH_API --> NEO

    SCORING --> PG
    HARVEST --> PG
